{"id":169240,"date":[{"year":1949,"month":11,"day":17}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"257","ytitle":"","mtitle":"刘老好换工小组","ftitle":"(根据地的一个生产组织。一九四五年苏北抗日民主)","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\11\\49bh070101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>进也能退，各人自愿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)“刘老好”动员换工，说:“能”</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\11\\49bh070102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(二)他叫男班做远工，女班做近工，好照顾家里伢儿吃奶做饭。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\11\\49bh070103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(三)小孩子没有劳动力，组织起来一起去挑青草。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\11\\49bh070104.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(四)买纱织布，大家都有衣裳穿。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\11\\49bh070105.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(五)没有耕牛，就组织拉犂班，怕人发笑，在晚上耕。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\11\\49bh070106.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(六)又叫全组割牛草，向人家换牛工，三亩半田，换牛草一担。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\11\\49bh070107.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(七)组员生了病，杀掉一口猪，请医生来看病。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1949\\11\\49bh070108.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(八)刘老好的换工小组真“老好”，全庄的人看得眼红，换工组都组织起来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除克　江有生　作</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>除克,江有生</FONT>"}]}